des:
This is a deprecated skill and will not be accepting new signups it is simply for maintaining older users. All new LED signups should move to the new home skill, https://www.amazon.com/Mr-CatNaps-LEDs/dp/B079PQJNTM.

Mr. CatNaps LEDs run off of ESP8266 microcomputers. They connect to the AWS IOT cloud and allow the user to control all the Mr. CatNaps LED functions. This skill requires me to manually add users to the database for their account linking to work, the new home skill does this all on the fly.
